<br>
First thing I would definitely change, get rid of the mushroom veil and find something that has a bit of hp, e.g. Crystal Eyes or Enshrouded Veil to name two of the cheaper and common items.  <br>
<br>
Second, find a replacement for your shoulders, you don't need that str, which you have more than enough for the time being.  A couple ideas for that slot are the various dragonwing pauldrons if you want to buy, slighted pauldrons if you want to get with a group in Maiden's Eye from the Battlemaster, of if you want to quest there is the Strength of Elements or Spirit Wracked Cords.<br>
<br>
Third, if you have the plat, go ahead and buy the parts for the PoTC, so you can get the Earring of the Solstice.  On the Tunare sever if you buy the individual parts instead of a whole package, you only spend about 9k to 10k pp, and you come out with a very nice earring, regardless of class.<br>
<br>
Finally, the last suggestion where you don't need to go and spend a ton of plat for upgrades, since you want more hp, drop the Glimmering Mithril Torque, and then replace it with a Clattering Bone Necklace, which sells on average for 2k to 3k pp on my server.<br>
<br>
Those should raise your hp by a few hundred hp, without spending a fortune.<br>
